在犹他大学就读博士的时候，纽维尔创建了犹他茶壶，<ref>{{citation
 | last = Torrence | first = Ann
 | contribution = Martin Newell's original teapot
 | doi = 10.1145/1180098.1180128
 | id = Article No. 29
 | isbn = 1-59593-364-6
 | location = New York, NY, USA
 | publisher = ACM
 | title = SIGGRAPH '06
 | year = 2006}}.</ref> 他还协助开发了用于[[渲染|渲染]]的[[画家算法|画家算法]]。他1975年毕业，1977至1979年在犹他研究院做研究。<ref name="uusc">[http://www.cs.utah.edu/dept/history/ History of the University of Utah School of Computing] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cs.utah.edu/dept/history/ |date=20131203035242 }}, retrieved 2010-01-26.</ref> 之后他到帕罗奥多研究中心，从事JaM的研究，JaM表示"John and Martin"，是[[PostScript|PostScript]]的前身，其中John是指[[约翰·沃诺克|约翰·沃诺克]]（John Warnock），Adobe公司的联合创始人。<ref>[http://knowledge.wharton.upenn.edu/article.cfm?articleid=2418 Adobe Co-founder John Warnock on the Competitive Advantages of Aesthetics and the 'Right' Technology] {{Wayback|url=http://knowledge.wharton.upenn.edu/article.cfm?articleid=2418 |date=20100703080544 }}, ''Knowledge@Wharton'', The Wharton School, January 20, 2010.</ref>

1988年，他创建了计算机辅助设计软件公司[[Ashlar|Ashlar]]。2007年，马丁·纽维尔成为[[美国国家工程院|美国国家工程院]]院士。<ref name="nae">[http://www.nae.edu/nae/naepub.nsf/e67ebaa6da15f1e685256a8400560624/adf4c9dce5bf342586257552006b374b?OpenDocument NAE member directory] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100528174218/http://www.nae.edu/nae/naepub.nsf/e67ebaa6da15f1e685256a8400560624/adf4c9dce5bf342586257552006b374b?OpenDocument |date=2010-05-28 }}, retrieved 2010-01-26.</ref> 他已经從Adobe公司退休。<ref name="nae"/>

